<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id78824be8-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s141"><num value="141">§ 141.</num><heading> Short title</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">This chapter may be cited as the “China Trade Act, 1922.”</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id78824be9-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/act/1922-09-19/ch346/s1">Sept. 19, 1922, ch. 346, § 1</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/42/849">42 Stat. 849</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id78824bea-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id78824beb-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I75" topic="referencesInText" id="id78824bec-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">This chapter, referred to in text, was in the original “this Act”, meaning <ref href="/us/act/1922-09-19/ch346">act Sept. 19, 1922, ch. 346</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/42/849">42 Stat. 849</ref>. The Act (except sections 21 to 27) is classified to this chapter. Sections 21 to 27 of the Act amended title II of the Revenue Act of 1921, which was repealed by section 1100 of the Revenue Act of 1924 (<ref href="/us/stat/43/352">43 Stat. 352</ref>).</p>
</note>
</notes>
